      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical wear-and-tear such as minor fluid seeps and a bit of suspension noise over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows clear signs of use including a few small tears in the upholstery. It has been recently serviced for basic maintenance, but it will likely require some minor mechanical attention in the near future to keep it in top shape.",
