    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or a donor car for parts. It suffers from significant mechanical problems, including a failing transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul. The exterior has noticeable rust, major paint peeling, and several dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It currently does not run reliably and will likely need to be towed. We are offering it at a low price to account for the extensive repairs needed.",
