      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! It drives beautifully and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle without breaking the bank. I've made sure to keep up with it, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner today. Feel free to message me if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m happy to answer any questions you have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
