    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The suspension geometry remains true with crisp turn-in and minimal body roll. The exterior and interior present well for its age, showing only minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car. This is a purist-spec machine optimized for tactile feedback and longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
